An Essentials add-on plugin that logs /pay and lets people access those logs with /transactions
http://dev.bukkit.org/server-mods/essentials/
http://ci.ess3.net/viewType.html?buildTypeId=bt2&guest=1
REQUIRES Essentials #Dev2.10.61 or higher 

Make sure you deny the essentials.pay permission and give people EssentialsPayLogger.pay to log payments.
